enhanced_by.reason: The iterator method relies on the collections added via addComposited for its iteration. Setting up the composite collection is crucial for the iterator to function correctly.
Clearing the composite collection can affect the state of the iterator. Testing the iterator method should consider scenarios where the collection is empty or has been cleared.
Removing a collection from the composite can affect the state of the iterator. Testing the iterator method should consider scenarios where collections are added and then removed.
Adding an element to the composite collection can affect the state of the iterator. Testing the iterator method should consider scenarios where elements are added dynamically.
